{"tid":617601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鉛水邨高铁出轨大桥烂尾，香港正式回归祖国","createTime":"2018-04-05T05:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T06:28:01.000Z","uid":21772,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"15318174f359143119bdd09af62dde07edd518c3","tid":617601,"uid":21772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:50:43.000Z","msg":"唔使講大家過去幾年都見到<br />\n香港過去幾年沉淪得幾快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經唔使講咩言論自由同法治<br />\n對掛住返工嘅香港人嚟講都係可有可無咁<br />\n但而家直頭想話「安份守己」<br />\n做港豬做順民都隨時健康同命仔不保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打開水喉飲鉛水冇件事<br />\n幾千億起橋起高鐵都可以搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過去幾年點差都好<br />\n都未去到話對所有基建都冇晒信心<br />\n而家邊個第日敢坐高鐵去港豬澳大橋真係要心口掛個勇字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾千億就咁倒落海<br />\n倒頭來唔止冇用係直頭冇得用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n似足支那鬼城一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放長雙眼又睇下三跑會唔會出事<br />\n越大鑊越快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e0e559f8ef6a8cd962c9b6ab5efb7092693f62","tid":617601,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:28:01.000Z","msg":"Wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}